sellerCard.oneLiner: Expert Logo, Branding, Graphic and Website Designer from Portugal
sellerCard.description: We are TI Design, a graphic design studio with a mission to shape a brighter future through the power of design. We are passionate about creating impactful visual communication that not only supports your organization's goals but also contributes to making the world a better place. Our team strives to deliver coherence and consistency in our designs, ensuring that your message reaches and resonates with your target audience.

description.content:
As a Professional Graphic Designer and the owner of TI Design, an excellent Fiverr studio based in Lisbon, I will create the perfect website for your company. My mission is to bring visibility and credibility to your organization by translating your message into a visual stand-out and professional website according to your needs.


Our Process:


  1. Consultation: Understand your needs and goals.
  2. Design Drafts: Initial concepts for your feedback.
  3. Refinement: Work closely for perfection.
  4. Development
  5. Launch & Support


You can expect with this gig:


  • Responsive design;
  • SEO optimized;
  • Secure;
  • Easy to use back-office;
  • Mobile responsiveness & optimization
  • No programming required;
  • 20% off your 1st year of Squarespace
  • Standard cookie banner
  • Logo to Favicon conversion (if you don't have a dedicated favicon)
  • Free stock images (if more images are needed)
  • (Premium stock or AI images available at additional costs)


Dedicated support provided up to two weeks after the release date in any package you buy!

questionsAndAnswers.question: What information do you need from me?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Once you place an order, you will be asked to answer a set of questions that will help us better understand what you want and need. You are also welcome to send me your brand's style guide if you have one.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What's a Website Landing Page?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: It's a single page website with all the information from the company and or product.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Which package should I order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Each package includes a different number of pages. You can find more details about it in the description.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Why should I work with you?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: We're specialized in developing Brand Identities & Website development. We love to work on interesting projects with great people like you! What are you waiting for?

questionsAndAnswers.question: My question is not here?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Please send us a private message with any other questions you might have :)

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can we discuss my project through a call or meeting on Fiverr?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, just ask for the calendar

questionsAndAnswers.question: How does it work with changes after project delivery?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Great question! After we wrap up the project in the Fiverr system, you’ve got 2 weeks to hit us up for any extra changes. Beyond that, changes shift into the new task category and will be subject to a minimum $50 charge. Thank you for understanding

questionsAndAnswers.question: What does revision mean and what does it include?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Revision is an iteration of design based on your suggestions/feedback. The revision includes implementations of all requested changes on the last design version delivered by the seller (me).

reviews.comment: Work was according to my description. would recommend.

I'm super happy with what Tiago and the team delivered for me. They redesigned my website exactly according to my brief and went the extra mile to implement the creative elements that I requested, which I think make my website stand out as compared to competitors. A big, big thanks to them!

Tiago was very easy to work with and provided a very quick turnaround to our project.  Would definitely recommend to others looking for a good value and a professional site.  I look forward to working with him and his team in the future.

J'ai eu beaucoup de difficulté à ce que toutes mes remarques soient prises en compte dans le rendu du site. J'ai parfois dû demander 3 fois des éléments, il y a même des points que j'ai dû abandonner car non pris en compte (inclusion de widgets depuis un autre site) ou alors j'ai moi-même fait les modifications sur Squarespace. J'ai eu l'impression que le but était de rendre dans les temps mais tant pis pour les détails. Je pense qu'il y a eu aussi la barrière de la langue. 
L'équipe est cependant toujours restée cordiale et le rapport qualité-prix est bien mais j'ai dû passer plus de temps à ré-expliquer ou modifier moi-même le site.

seller_response.comment:
Thank you for your review
It was indeed not a smooth project, with lots of revisions and scattered feedback, and request for additionals which came along the way. I still believe that you have received a stellar 2 websites for only 700 USD
A bit disappointed on the 3.3 star review though, for this price and services we have offered.
All the best with your business!
Tiago
